.SH REPORTING BUGS
Please report bugs to <http://bugs.cihar.com>.

Before reporting a bug, please enable verbose logging in SMSD configuration:

    [gammu]
    logformat = textall

    [smsd]
    debuglevel = 255
    logfile = smsd.log

and include this verbose log within bug report.
